### Agent frontmatter format
```yaml
---
name: agent-name
description: |
  Use this agent when...

  <example>
  Context: ...
  user: "..."
  assistant: "..."
  <commentary>...</commentary>
  </example>
model: sonnet
---
```

### Skill frontmatter format
```yaml
---
name: skill-name
description: Use when the user asks to "...", "...", or needs "..."
---
```

